And don't forget to read the Creating your Character Guidelines, Transformation Guidelines, How to Role Play. We offer lots of helpful advice to newcomers to the roleplay scene.

items.headline: Dragon Ball Z Knowledge Communities
items.desc: Looking at the fan community surrounding the popular anime series. This describes what a knowledge community is, how Dragon Ball Z relates to it and a few analyses of some concepts of communities. The analysis includes the how it is a knowledge community, the interperative disputes which surround the community and how it has been refashioned.
